Keri Lynn Pratt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keri_Lynn_Pratt 0 Keri Lynn Pratt (born September 23, 1978) is an American actress of film and television. She is well known for her role of Missy Belknap on Jack Bobby and as Dee Vine in the film Drive Me Crazy, which was her debut role.
